    {
        "content": "<p>avanhatt updated <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550\">PR #13550</a>.</p>",
        "id": 603440406,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1781543597
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550#issuecomment-4710411502\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550\">PR #13550</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for your last commit -- looks like the dep bumps and vet burden are real; still 425163 LoC.</p>\n<p>Digging into one particular bump (<code>tracing 0.1.41 -&gt; 0.1.44</code>, which alone is 61kLoC of diff), it looks like the aslp crate depends on tracing too, and probably pulled in a newer version somehow?</p>\n<p>Would you mind doing a little dep gardening to see if we can get the diff to our deps a bit smaller? <code>cargo vet</code> should work locally for anyone to check the audit backlog size, too. Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 603440465,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1781543608
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>mmcloughlin updated <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550\">PR #13550</a>.</p>",
        "id": 603521528,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1781563318
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>mmcloughlin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550#issuecomment-4713104144\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550\">PR #13550</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Would you mind doing a little dep gardening</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Done and pushed. I see 7 unvetted dependencies in <code>cargo vet</code> now. Some appear to be partially covered already trusted authors. The biggest remaining one is <code>pest</code>, which I think may fall under the \"10,000 downloads a day\" policy.</p>\n<p>Let us know if you see the same, and the backlog is manageable.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 603523040,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1781563823
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>avanhatt updated <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550\">PR #13550</a>.</p>",
